---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'

const t1 = 'The back bone of our company is our supervisory staff. Our reputation is built on the fact that we provide our clients with field supervisors at no cost to them. Most companies either reduce the supervision or charge for it.'

const t2 = 'The old saying “You get what you pay for” does not apply at National 50 Security, not only do we provide field and management supervision at no cost to the client but we supply the finest supervisors in the industry. All of our supervisors are licensed professionals dedicated to assuring that our clients are provided the best security available. All of our supervisors have an abundance of experience in supervision and security and pride themselves on the outstanding performance of those they supervise.'

---

        {/* White Section - Mission Statement*/}
        <section class="bg-white px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 md:py-16 lg:px-8">
          <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-md lg:max-w-screen-xl">
            
            {/* Project description */}
            <div class="mx-auto mt-6 flex w-full flex-wrap">
              <div class="grid grid-cols-2">
                <div class="mx-auto w-full">
                  <div class="flex w-full mb-8">
                    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-dark-900">FIELD SUPERVISORS</h1>
                  </div>
                  <p
                    class="mb-6 text-1xl font-normal tracking-tight text-dark-900 lg:leading-tight"
                  >
                    {t1.toUpperCase()}
                  </p>
                  <p
                    class="mb-6 text-1xl font-normal tracking-tight text-dark-900 lg:leading-tight"
                  >
                    {t2.toUpperCase()}
                  </p>
                  
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div class="pl-8 m-auto">
                    <Image
                      src='https://html.tonatheme.com/wp/bristol/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/video-image.jpg'
                      width= {600}
                      height={500}
                      alt='Our Employees'
                      class="h-auto rounded-3xl object-cover object-center shadow-xl"
                    />
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>